Symbol.Script_3D:
! Sand Filter
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
IF mbShow THEN
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT 0, A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN lowerArcRad = ((A/2-footingUWidth/2)^2+lowerArcHeight^2)/(2*(A/2-footingUWidth/2)) beta = ASN(lowerArcHeight/lowerArcRad)
CONE footingHeight, footingLWidth/2, footingUWidth/2, 90, 90
ROTy -90 PUT footingHeight, footingUWidth/2, 1 num = 3 alpha_i = beta/num: alpha = 90-beta FOR i = 1 TO num alpha = alpha+alpha_i PUT footingHeight+lowerArcHeight-lowerArcRad*COS(alpha), A/2-lowerArcRad+lowerArcRad*SIN(alpha), 1 NEXT i
num = 4 alpha_i = 90/num: alpha = 0 FOR i = 1 TO num+1 PUT ZZYZX-arcRad+arcRad*SIN(alpha), A/2-arcRad+arcRad*COS(alpha), 1 alpha = alpha+alpha_i NEXT i
REVOLVE NSP/3, 360, 1+2+16+32, GET (NSP) DEL 1 ELSE CYLIND ZZYZX, A/2 ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
RESOL res CUTPOLYA 2, 2, 0, 0, 0, 979, A/2, 360, 4079
IF ConStatus_1 THEN ! --- PIPE INLET CONNECTION --- ! ADDz ConPosZ_1 ROTy -90 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, A/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_1/2, 360, 4001 DEL 2 ENDIF
IF ConStatus_2 THEN ! --- PIPE OUTLET CONNECTION --- ! ADDz ConPosZ_2 ROTy -90 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, A/2, 16, 0, 0, 901, ConWidth_2/2, 360, 4001 DEL 2 ENDIF CUTEND ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 14, ConEdgeVisible_1 = 0, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 14, ConEdgeVisible_2 = 0 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Sand Filter
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 0, A/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -A/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
PUT 0, 0, 901, A/2, 360, 4001
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
IF ConStatus_2 THEN ! --- PIPE OUTLET CONNECTION --- !
PUT -A/2, 0, 1, 0, 1, 801, -SQR((A/2)^2-(ConWidth_2/2)^2), ConWidth_2/2, 1001, -A/2, ConWidth_2/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT -A/2, 0, 1, 0, -1, 801, -SQR((A/2)^2-(ConWidth_2/2)^2), -ConWidth_2/2, 1001, -A/2, -ConWidth_2/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF
IF ConStatus_1 THEN ! --- PIPE INLET CONNECTION --- !
PUT -A/2, 0, 1, 0, 1, 801, -SQR((A/2)^2-(ConWidth_1/2)^2), ConWidth_1/2, 1001, -A/2, ConWidth_1/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT -A/2, 0, 1, 0, -1, 801, -SQR((A/2)^2-(ConWidth_1/2)^2), -ConWidth_1/2, 1001, -A/2, -ConWidth_1/2, 0
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF
SET FILL gs_fill_type
PEN gs_cont_pen IF gs_fill_pen THEN PEN gs_fill_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 3+32, 4, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1, mbShow = 0 PEN gs_cont_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 2, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1, mbShow = 0 ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConShow_1 = 0, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConEdgeVisible_1 = 0, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConShow_2 = 0, ConEdit_2 = 1, ConEdgeVisible_2 = 0 DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Sand Filter
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
arcRad = 0.15 lowerArcHeight = arcRad-0.02 footingHeight = 0.10 footingLWidth = A-0.10 footingUWidth = footingLWidth-0.07
z = 0
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z
Symbol.Script_UI:
! Sand Filter
UI_DIALOG `Специальные Параметры MEP`
DIM ui_vis_attr[4][4] FOR i = 1 TO 4 FOR j = 1 TO 4 ui_vis_attr[i][j] = 0 NEXT j NEXT i ui_vis_attr[1][1] = 2 ui_vis_attr[1][2] = 1 ui_vis_attr[1][3] = 7
ui_vis_attr[2][1] = 1 ui_vis_attr[2][2] = 237 ui_vis_attr[2][3] = 68 ui_vis_attr[2][4] = 14
DIM ui_con_type[2] ui_con_type[1] = 0 ui_con_type[2] = 0
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS ALL ui_vis_attr = ui_vis_attr, ui_centerline_vars = 0, ui_con_type = ui_con_type, ui_system_var_pos = 2, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
Symbol.Script_VL:
! Sand Filter
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 0 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
! --- MAIN PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF A < arcRad*2+0.01 THEN A = arcRad*2+0.01 VALUES "A" RANGE [arcRad*2+0.01,] IF ZZYZX < arcRad+lowerArcHeight+footingHeight+ConWidth_1+ConWidth_2 THEN ZZYZX = arcRad+lowerArcHeight+footingHeight+ConWidth_1+ConWidth_2 VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [arcRad+lowerArcHeight+footingHeight+ConWidth_1+ConWidth_2,] ENDIF
B = A PARAMETERS B = B
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
PARAMETERS MEP_NumberConnections = 2
! --- PIPE INLET CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 1 ConName = `Труба Впускного Соединения `
ConDVecX = -1 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 0
ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = -1 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF ConWidth_1 > MIN(A/2, ZZYZX-arcRad-lowerArcHeight-footingHeight-ConWidth_2) THEN ConWidth_1 = MIN(A/2, ZZYZX-arcRad-lowerArcHeight-footingHeight-ConWidth_2) VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE (0, MIN(A/2, ZZYZX-arcRad-lowerArcHeight-footingHeight-ConWidth_2)] PARAMETERS ConDepth_1 = ConWidth_1 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_1"
IF ConPosZ_1 > ZZYZX-arcRad-ConWidth_1/2 THEN ConPosZ_1 = ZZYZX-arcRad-ConWidth_1/2 IF ConStatus_2 THEN VALUES "ConPosZ_1" RANGE [ConPosZ_2+ConWidth_2/2+ConWidth_1/2, ZZYZX-arcRad-ConWidth_1/2] ELSE VALUES "ConPosZ_1" RANGE [footingHeight+lowerArcHeight+ConWidth_1/2, ZZYZX-arcRad-ConWidth_1/2] ENDIF VALUES "ConLength_1" RANGE [0, ]
PARAMETERS ConPosX_1 = -B/2 PARAMETERS ConPosY_1 = 0 ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
! --- UPPER SIDE CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 2 ConName = `Труба Выпускного Соединения`
ConDVecX = -1 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 0
ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = -1 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF ConWidth_2 > MIN(A/2, ZZYZX-arcRad-lowerArcHeight-footingHeight-ConWidth_1) THEN ConWidth_2 = MIN(A/2, ZZYZX-arcRad-lowerArcHeight-footingHeight-ConWidth_1) VALUES "ConWidth_2" RANGE (0, MIN(A/2, ZZYZX-arcRad-lowerArcHeight-footingHeight-ConWidth_1)] PARAMETERS ConDepth_2 = ConWidth_2 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_2"
IF ConStatus_1 THEN IF ConPosZ_2 > ConPosZ_1-ConWidth_1/2-ConWidth_2/2 THEN ConPosZ_2 = ConPosZ_1-ConWidth_1/2-ConWidth_2/2 VALUES "ConPosZ_2" RANGE [footingHeight+lowerArcHeight+ConWidth_2/2, ConPosZ_1-ConWidth_1/2-ConWidth_2/2] ELSE IF ConPosZ_2 > ZZYZX-arcRad-ConWidth_2/2 THEN ConPosZ_2 = ZZYZX-arcRad-ConWidth_2/2 VALUES "ConPosZ_2" RANGE [footingHeight+lowerArcHeight+ConWidth_2/2, ZZYZX-arcRad-ConWidth_2/2] ENDIF VALUES "ConLength_2" RANGE [0, ]
PARAMETERS ConPosX_2 = -B/2 PARAMETERS ConPosY_2 = 0 ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_2, ConPosY = ConPosY_2, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_2, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_2, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_2, ConWidth = ConWidth_2, ConDepth = ConDepth_2, ConLength = ConLength_2, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_2, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_2, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_2, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_2, ConToolType = ConToolType_2, ConStatus = ConStatus_2, ConType_2 = ConType_2, ConConnectorType_2 = ConConnectorType_2, ConSystem_2 = ConSystem_2, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_2, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF setProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
